import React, { useState, useContext, useEffect } from 'react' import { Link, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import flightContent from "../context/FlightContext"; import '../styles/Dashboard.css' import { useAuth } from '.././context/Auth' import axios from 'axios'; const Dashboard = () => { const [auth] = useAuth() const host = "http://localhost:4000" const content = useContext(flightContent) const { setFetchBooking, setFetchPassenger } = content const navigate = useNavigate() const viewBooking = async (bid) => { const response = await fetch(`${host}/api/v1/auth/myflight?_id=${bid}`, { method: 'GET', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'auth-token': auth.token, } }); const pbdata = await response.json() if (pbdata.success) { setFetchBooking(pbdata.flights) const response = await fetch(`${host}/api/v1/auth/getpassofbook?_id=${bid}`, { method: 'GET', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'auth-token': auth.token, } }) const bpdata = await response.json() if (bpdata.success) { setFetchPassenger(bpdata.passenger) navigate('/fetchbooking') } } } const [bookings, setBookings] = useState([]) const getBookingsWU = async () => { const { data } = await axios.get('/auth/myflights') setBookings(data.flights) } useEffect(() => { getBookingsWU() }, []) return (
